{"tid":2449831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［劣根性］ 支那少年 連酒店電腦嘅display card 都要偷","createTime":"2021-03-17T03:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T04:52:26.000Z","uid":374134,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"53d7293f0670a3030d665d3840e8ae2b06a386d0","tid":2449831,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"在早年電競熱潮下，務求吸引年輕一代目光大量商鋪都為自己增加電競要素，而在重慶中就有一名小偷因近期顯卡短暫的問題，<strong>入往電競酒店時利用舊款 GTX 650 Ti 顯示卡，</strong><span class=\"gold\">成功偷天換日帶走房間內主機的 RTX 2070 顯示卡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZphRo0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZphRo0.jpg&h=d5a5574b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據重慶晨報的報導，某間電競酒店在客人投訴房間內的電腦無法正啟動，員工將鬆動的電源線重新連接後，發現畫面的亮度與房間的另一電腦不同，<span class=\"green\">於是打開機箱後發現機內顯示卡被換，</span><strong>在報警後再透過監視鏡頭將數日前入住的小偷繩之於法。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而小偷被捕後，指自己留意到近期 RTX 顯卡短暫的問題，認為可以借以這個機會去從中找到「財路」，</strong><span class=\"gold\">但他以為電腦沒有顯示卡就無法啟動</span>，<span class=\"green\">於是在入住當日附近電腦店以 300 人民幣購買了一張 GTX 650 Ti Boost ，再將酒店電腦中的 RTX 2070 交換</span>，<span class=\"gold\">並即日以 2,900 人民幣賣走</span>，再於酒店居住一日掩人耳目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814adcaebf8f80ceac907414dadc826483a5ec0f","tid":2449831,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">[member]https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/chinese-theif-stole-rtx-display-card-and-replace-with-gtx/[/member]</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a3c51ca3411e93823b2a7d58204d7eac83cd2fa2","tid":2449831,"uid":238920,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:30:15.000Z","msg":"重點係房入面有CCTV"},{"pid":"2a7f7a0017889d1d3516089a88b9e90366a3c8e6","tid":2449831,"uid":2521,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"酒店房入面有cam咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2902441cb7c